      "span_text": "There is limited information about testing HCV RNA at W12 post-treatment to evaluate SVR in HIV/HCV co-infected patients and studies are needed to clarify this issue.  The objective of this study was to evaluate if measuring serum HCV RNA at W12 is as informative as at W24 to predict SVR in HIV/HCV co-infected patients with a virological end of treatment response (ETR).",
